SUMMARY:Bewonersavond Noord - de Banne
DTSTART;TZID=W. Europe Standard Time:20260506T180000
DTEND;TZID=W. Europe Standard Time:20260506T210000
CLASS:PUBLIC
PRIORITY:5
DTSTAMP:20260429T033950Z
TRANSP:OPAQUE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SEQUENCE:1
LOCATION:Huis van de Wijk de Banne (Bezaanjachtplein 243\, 1034 CR Amsterdam Noord-Holland\, Nederland)
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-APPT-SEQUENCE:1
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-BUSYSTATUS:BUSY
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-INTENDEDSTATUS:BUSY
